title: Senzala Creperie
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Western, French, Brazilian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Offers a range of vegetarian and labeled vegan savory and dessert crepes. Each item can be made with either a crepe or galette (the buckwheat based, vegan version of the traditional crepe). Dessert options are extensive and can be made using a galette base and any of the vegan toppings (not labelled) such as fruit, spreads/preserves or traditional lemon and sugar.
